Privacy Policy for Comedy Night
Effective Date: 3 July 2023
1. Introduction
Welcome to Comedy Night, a game developed by Lighthouse Games Studio. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information while you use our game. By playing Comedy Night, you agree to the collection and use of your data as outlined in this policy.
2. Information We Collect
a. Gameplay Data:
We collect gameplay data, including but not limited to Rooms joined, Â Room Names you created/updated and Room Descriptions. This data helps us improve your gaming experience and ensure the smooth operation of the game.
b. User-Generated Content:
Any content you submit in-game, such as any social networks you choose to display on your profile, player ratings, player toxicity reports, room descriptions, rooms joined, session length, and other user-generated content like Face Masks & Stage Background, is stored on our servers.
c. In-App Purchases (IAP) and Video Advertisements:
We integrate video ads and in-app purchases within the game. We use Unity for displaying video advertisements and handling crash analytics. Unity may collect certain information to serve ads and improve their services.
3. How We Use Your Information
a. Improving Gameplay:
The data we collect helps us enhance your gaming experience by providing better game features, addressing bugs, and optimizing game performance.
b. Serving Ads:
We use Unity to display in-game video advertisements. Unity may use the data they collect to serve personalized ads based on your gameplay behavior.
c. Crash Analytics:
We utilize Unity's crash analytics to identify and resolve technical issues, ensuring a smoother gaming experience.
4. Data Sharing and Third Parties
Data collected by Lighthouse Games Studio is not shared with any third parties. However, Unity, as a third-party service provider, collects and processes data for advertising and analytics purposes. We use Google Firebase to send push notifications.
5. Data Security
We take the security of your data seriously. Appropriate measures are in place to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
6. Children's Privacy
Comedy Night is not directed at children under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 16. If we become aware that we have collected such information, we will take steps to delete it as soon as possible.
7. Your Data Rights
You have the right to delete the personal data we have collected about you. If you have any requests or concerns regarding your data, please contact us at
contact@LighthouseGamesStudio.com
. You can request to delete your account from the Settings menu in the game.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of Comedy Night after any modifications indicates your acceptance of the new terms.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: contact@LighthouseGamesStudio.com
Thank you for playing Comedy Night!